---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'Is this a religious thing?',
    answer: 'Grove is run by Christians, and our faith shapes why we care about mentoring students. But we\'re not here to preach at you or make anything weird. We lead with genuine value—good projects, real mentorship, actual community. Relationships form naturally over time. No pressure, no awkward conversations, no strings attached.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Do I need to be experienced?',
    answer: 'Nope. If you can write a basic function and use git, you\'re ready. Our projects have issues tagged by difficulty level, and mentors are here to help you level up. That said, this isn\'t a "learn to code" program—we expect you to be learning that through school or on your own. We\'re here to give you real-world practice.'
  },
  {
    question: 'What\'s the time commitment?',
    answer: 'Totally flexible. Some folks contribute a few hours a week, others go deep on weekends. There are no minimums or deadlines. This is async-friendly and designed to work around your class schedule. The more you put in, the more you\'ll get out—but even small contributions add up over time.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Is this actually free?',
    answer: 'Yes, 100%. No fees, no hidden costs, no catch. The projects we work on serve real communities, and the work you do has genuine impact. We\'re not a company making money off student labor. We\'re engineers who want to help the next generation succeed.'
  },
  {
    question: 'What if I\'m not a CS major?',
    answer: 'That\'s fine! If you\'re learning to code and want real project experience, you\'re welcome here. Some of the best engineers we know came from non-traditional paths. What matters is curiosity and follow-through, not what department you\'re in.'
  }
];
---

<section id="faq" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-warm-50">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">
        Frequently asked questions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-warm-600">
        Straight answers to the things people actually wonder about.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ List -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      {faqs.map((faq, index) => (
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-warm-200 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 text-left">{faq.question}</h3>
            <svg 
              class="w-5 h-5 text-warm-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" 
              fill="none" 
              stroke="currentColor" 
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">{faq.answer}</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- More questions -->
    <p class="text-center mt-12 text-warm-500">
      Got more questions? <a href="#join" class="text-grove-600 hover:underline">Ask us on Discord</a>—we're friendly.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
